     C* E8: F-spec device SPECIAL has no codegen support and must
     C* be a hard compile error, not a silent flat-file miscompile.
     C* (WORKSTN is exempt from E8 -- see neg_workstn.rpg, now a
     C* positive WORKSTN test -- but SPECIAL/CONSOLE still hard-error.)
     FSPDATA  IP  F    80              SPECIAL
     CLR                   SETOF
